<!DOCTYPE html>


<body>
	<style>
		background-image: url("https://encrypted-tbn2.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSF7Wp6EeOa1Eb0Cq9rnsCFYfJbeJcu0MwAF0-vTzlstVoub4Nu8w");
	</style>

	<div class="Main_Massage">
        <h1>Welcome to your best source for Crowdfunding renewable energy projects</h1>
		<h3>Bringing together companies in need of capital, with potential investors and insurance companies to reduce risks</h3>

       
		<h4> Already a member - sign in <%= link_to "here", home_path %> </h4>
      </div>
	  
	 <div class="Fancy_wrapper">
		<div class="row-fluid lower_body">
		
		<div class="span4">
			
			<div class="secondary_massage">
				<a class="btn btn-large btn-success " href="#">A new investor</a> 	  
				<h3>Why should you invest through this platform</h3>
			</div>
			
			 <div class="row">
				 <dl>
					<dt>Great visibility into the companies asking for funding</dt>
					<dd>You can see the track record of the company asking for funding, as well as the current project's detailed insurance and return plans</dd>
					<dt>Multiple options to invest, both in higher and lower risk ventures</dt>
					<dd>On one side, ability to invest in projects that are already built and insured, and just more money for opperations.
					    On the other side, ability to invest in a proof of concept, or at the initial construction of the projects.</dd>
					<dt>Invest in a growing and maturing industry</dt>
					<dd>Trends show that the cost of renewable energy technologies will continue to decrease 
					     faster than conventional energy technologies as the renewable sector matures.</dd>

				</dl>

				
			  </div>
		</div>	
			 
		<div class="span4">
			   <div class="secondary_massage">
					<a class="btn btn-large btn-success" href="#">A new funds-seeker</a> 
					<h3>Why should you look for investment here</h3>
				</div>
			
			 <div class="row">
				 <dl>
					<dt>A good way to receive funding at different stages of the project</dt>
					<dd>Ask for funding for all phases of the project: From proof of concept, to infrastracture, 
					    to buying insurance and finally for the ongoing operation of the project</dd>
					<dt>Gain credit and reduce your future insurance costs</dt>
					<dd>We work with a number of large insurance companies, and have come to an agreement with them that 
					   companies that show a solid track record will getter better insurance rates.
						In addition, once a good trace record is established, lesser equity can be granted in the earlier phases of the project</dd>
					


				</dl>
			
			</div>
		 </div>
		 
		 <div class="span4">
			   <div class="secondary_massage">
					<a class="btn btn-large btn-success" href="#">A new insurance company</a> 
					<h3>Why should you look for clients here</h3>
				</div>
			
			 <div class="row">
				 <dl>
					<dt>Get access to promising companies at an early stage</dt>
					<dd>As a member of our insurance company portfolio you will manage to get access to many new 
					    early stage renewable energy companies that will later grow into much larger companies that will 
						require match larger insurance policies</dd>
					<dt>View track record of companies</dt>
					<dd>Our platform aims to be as transparent as possible, enabling an insurance company to look at the track record of the company, 
						thereby understanding whether the company is capable of the tasks at hand. This greatly reduces some of the uncertenties of 
						insuring renewable energy project at an early stage</dd>


				</dl>
			
			</div>
		 
		</div>
   	</div>

	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

	<script>

					(function() {
						$(this)
								.next()
									.slideDown(200);
									
						$('dd').filter(':nth-child(n+4)').addClass('hide');

						$('dl').on('mouseenter', 'dt', function() {
							$(this)
								.next()
									.slideDown(200)
									.siblings('dd')
										.slideUp(200);
						});
					})();


	</script>	
   
</body>
 
	
	  